  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.packt.neuralnet.data.DataNormalization

  • public class DataNormalization
extends java.lang.Object
    DataNormalization This abstract class allows normalize and denormalize data via MIN_MAX, AVG_STDDEV, MINUSONE_PLUSONE, MINUSTWO_PLUSTWO techniques
